  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<section class=\"webinar-detail\">\n<div class=\"webinar-hero-banner hero__container hero__container--text-dark hero__container--no-overlay hero__container--color\">\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<h1 class=\"webinar-title\">\n<span>Workplace Violence: Evolving Risks and Rising Claims</span>\n</h1>\n<span data-item-id=\"80675\" data-price=\"64.00\" data-product=\"Workplace Violence: Evolving Risks and Rising Claims\" data-react-component-id=\"add-to-cart\">\n<button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--disabled\">Add to Cart -\t\t\t\t\t\t&amp;dollar;64.00</button>\n</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width container__flex u-padding-top\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark badge--icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-icon-calendar-dims\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#calendar\"></use>\n</svg>\n<div><time datetime=\"2026-02-24T18:00:00Z\">Feb. 24 2026 01:00 PM EST</time>\n</div>\n</span>\n<div class=\"webinar-block u-margin-bottom\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"webinar-description u-padding-bottom\">\n<p>Workplace violence is no longer limited to physical altercations—it now spans verbal abuse, cyber harassment, and even virtual threats. Examine how shifting definitions, emerging legal trends, and expanded mental health compensability are reshaping workers’ compensation. Analyze why policies often fail, assess compensability challenges, and uncover prevention strategies that actually work. Through case-based discussion and actionable takeaways, you’ll strengthen your ability to evaluate, manage, and mitigate violence-related claims while protecting the well-being of claims teams and improving organizational resilience.</p><ul><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $64.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span><ul><li><em>*CEU Unlimited subscriber webinar discount will be reflected in the checkout pr